# ICP

<!-- What makes a candidate worth a human's attention. The agent scores candidates against
     this in the Qualify stage. Be concrete — vague criteria pass everyone. -->

- **Who:** <the entity you target — a person, an account, a post>
- **Signal:** <what says "worth engaging now" — reach, topic, timing, pain>
- **Fit:** <why this candidate serves the goal>
- **Disqualifiers:** <hard nos>
